00:59:15.455 --> 00:59:28.740 align:middle line:90%


00:59:28.740 --> 00:59:33.060 align:middle line:84%
So this is the final
word in today's story

00:59:33.060 --> 00:59:35.260 align:middle line:84%
about what we can say
about paths of length 2.

